OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1781718499
OL,3,CLabour calls for shadow minister to be
OL,4,Csacked over PM arson attack 'joke'
OL,6,FLabour Party chairwoman Anna Turley
OL,7,Falso called on Tory leader Kemi
OL,8,FBadenoch to sack her shadow minister
OL,9,Fover the appearance, which came on the
OL,10,Fanniversary of the murder of Labour MP
OL,11,FJo Cox.
OL,13,FA Conservative Party spokesman
OL,14,Finsisted Mr Vickers did not "actually
OL,15,Fsay anything wrong" and was laughing
OL,16,Fto be "polite to the host of a radio
OL,17,Fprogramme".
OL,26,@vD@]OUwD@SO]xD@GOUyD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/11
