OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1781718499
OL,3,CLabour calls for shadow minister to be
OL,4,Csacked over PM arson attack 'joke'
OL,6,FMr Vickers, who is the Tory deputy
OL,7,Fchairman, appeared on Talk TV on
OL,8,FTuesday, where he was asked by host
OL,9,FJeremy Kyle for his thoughts on the
OL,10,Fsentencing of two men found guilty of
OL,11,Farson attacks on a property and a car
OL,12,Fconnected to Sir Keir Starmer.
OL,14,FIt followed reports that both men may
OL,15,Fhave operated under instruction from
OL,16,Fan online handler linked to Russia.
OL,18,FMr Kyle said that Russia had also
OL,19,F"started the conspiracy theory that it
OL,20,Fwas revenge by two Ukrainian rent
OL,21,Fboys".
OL,26,@{D@AOU}D@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1781718499
OL,3,CLabour calls for shadow minister to be
OL,4,Csacked over PM arson attack 'joke'
OL,6,FMr Vickers said: "There is a serious
OL,7,Fpoint, isn't there, about the
OL,8,Fdangerous world we live in, Russian
OL,9,Finfluence, and actually the security
OL,10,Fof people in public life ` the thing
OL,11,Fwe remind of, it's 10 years since Jo
OL,12,FCox died.
OL,14,F"But the idea that there's some
OL,15,FRussian secret effort to destabilise
OL,16,Fthe country via the Prime Minister ` I
OL,17,Fmean, you'd leave him in office and
OL,18,Flet him destroy the country.
OL,26,@nD@ROUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1781718499
OL,3,CLabour calls for shadow minister to be
OL,4,Csacked over PM arson attack 'joke'
OL,6,F"You'd stop distracting him, because
OL,7,Fhe's kind of doing a canny job of
OL,8,Fblowing himself up."
OL,10,FAsked again whether the men were "rent
OL,11,Fboys", Mr Vickers laughed, saying he
OL,12,Fwas "not familiar with them".
OL,14,FMr Lammy said the shadow minister
OL,15,F"laughed along to demeaning homophobic
OL,16,Fremarks" during the interview.
OL,18,FDeputy Prime Minister David Lammy told
OL,19,FMatt Vickers he should "grow up" and
OL,20,Fapologise for making jokes about an
OL,21,Fattack on the PM's home
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@TO]rD@bOUsD@EO]tD@EOUtD@\O]wD@
OL,26,AAOUxD@HO]{D@XOU{D@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1781718499
OL,3,CLabour calls for shadow minister to be
OL,4,Csacked over PM arson attack 'joke'
OL,6,FReferring to the attack on Sir Keir's
OL,7,Fproperty, Mr Kyle said "it wasn't his
OL,8,Fback door, it was his front door" that
OL,9,Fwas targeted, and the Prime Minister
OL,10,Fwas also bringing in a social media
OL,11,Fban for under 16s "through the back
OL,12,Fdoor", which the Tory deputy chairman
OL,13,Falso laughed at, saying "god, Jezza".
OL,15,FThe deputy Prime Minister launched his
OL,16,Fattack on Mr Vickers while responding
OL,17,Fto a question during Deputy PMQs, with
OL,18,Fthe shadow minister criticising the
OL,19,FGovernment's economic record.
OL,26,@oD@XOUpD@aO]sD@SOUtD@EO]uD@YOUuD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1781718499
OL,3,CLabour calls for shadow minister to be
OL,4,Csacked over PM arson attack 'joke'
OL,6,FMr Lammy said: "We've got the fastest
OL,7,Fgrowing economy in the G7, borrowing
OL,8,Fis down, and we just signed our fifth
OL,9,Fmajor trade deal.
OL,11,F"But, I must say to this Tory deputy
OL,12,Fchairman, yesterday he was on
OL,13,Ftelevision laughing and joking about
OL,14,Fthe arson attack on the Prime
OL,15,FMinister's home.
OL,26,@nD@POUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1781718499
OL,3,CLabour calls for shadow minister to be
OL,4,Csacked over PM arson attack 'joke'
OL,6,F"Laughing about a fire bomb targeting
OL,7,Fthe Prime Minister and his family, not
OL,8,Fonly that, he joined with promoting
OL,9,Fconspiracies about the attack and
OL,10,Flaughed along to demeaning homophobic
OL,11,Fremarks he should be ashamed of.
OL,13,F"My advice to him is to grow up,
OL,14,Fapologise, and do considerably better."
OL,16,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUvD@gO]
