FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1781718499
OL,3,CLabour calls for shadow minister to be
OL,4,Csacked over PM arson attack 'joke'
OL,6,FA Conservative spokesman said: "If you
OL,7,Flisten to what Matt Vickers says, he
OL,8,Fdoesn't actually say anything wrong in
OL,9,Fthe clip.
OL,11,F"If you've got an issue with the
OL,12,Fcontent of the programme or what
OL,13,FJeremy Kyle says, I suggest taking
OL,14,Fthat with Jeremy Kyle."
OL,16,FAsked why he laughed along and did not
OL,17,Fchallenge Kyle, the spokesman said:
OL,18,F"He's trying to be polite to the host
OL,19,Fof a radio programme."
OL,26,@nD@`OUsD@AOUvD@WO]zD@AOU{D@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G9/11
