PN,39110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1781718499
OL,3,CLabour calls for shadow minister to be
OL,4,Csacked over PM arson attack 'joke'
OL,6,FLabour Party chairwoman Anna Turley
OL,7,Fsaid: "It is frankly sickening that
OL,8,Fanyone would seek to laugh and joke
OL,9,Fabout an appalling attack on a fellow
OL,10,Fpolitician's family home.
OL,12,F"To do so on the same day as we stood
OL,13,Fin unity to mark the anniversary of
OL,14,Four dear friend and much-missed
OL,15,Fcolleague Jo Cox, is beyond the pale.
OL,26,@oD@GOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G10/11
