PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1781718499
OL,3,CLabour calls for shadow minister to be
OL,4,Csacked over PM arson attack 'joke'
OL,6,F"Matt Vickers is not fit to be an MP
OL,7,Fand if Kemi Badenoch had an ounce of
OL,8,Fintegrity or respect for the safety of
OL,9,Fthose who seek to serve the public,
OL,10,Fshe would do the right thing and sack
OL,11,Fhim today."
